        "TileImage": "$($repository 3e3e3752-37db-4b0f-8ff3-827d4c565e55).Image",
        "Description": "Good morning, 47.\rOur client is a veteran art technician who has worked on projects across the globe, from famous Bollywood film sets to clandestine Berlin nightclubs. Though their work is well renowned, they are not.\rOver the years their work has been plagerised by various big names in the artistic world, gaining the fame our client feels they deserve. We&apos;ve been contracted with turning the lights out on these bright stars during their latest stolen project reveal in Dubai.\rGood luck, 47.",
